446
00:19:22,924 --> 00:19:25,483
but you blame the Yueluo people instead.

447
00:19:25,983 --> 00:19:28,164
Because they are weaker, right?

448
00:19:28,944 --> 00:19:30,823
You claimed that you wanted
to go to Yueluo.

449
00:19:31,384 --> 00:19:32,983
