677
00:31:34,464 --> 00:31:36,364
from the war.

678
00:31:38,483 --> 00:31:39,924
However,

679
00:31:40,523 --> 00:31:41,763
the late Emperor suddenly fell ill,

680
00:31:42,884 --> 00:31:44,763
