possibly abduct him?

692
00:32:05,303 --> 00:32:06,384
You, on the other hand,

693
00:32:06,864 --> 00:32:07,724
changed your name

694
00:32:07,724 --> 00:32:08,604
and fled to Wei State.

695
00:32:09,263 --> 00:32:11,063
You must be related
to Prince Qi's death.

696
00:32:13,404 --> 00:32:15,384
It's the Yan sisters.

697
00:32:17,543 --> 00:32:18,644
Yan sisters?

698
00:32:19,144 --> 00:32:20,743
They disguised themselves
as maidservants

699
00:32:20,843 --> 00:32:22,164
and hid beside Prince Qi.

700
00:32:22,404 --> 00:32:24,604
They were actually assassins
sent by Wei State.

701
00:32:25,624 --> 00:32:27,864
I only found out
about their true identities

702
00:32:27,964 --> 00:32:30,563
after some time in Wei.

703
00:32:34,323 --> 00:32:35,364
It's true, sir.

704
00:32:36,704 --> 00:32:39,283
There was one night when I was
on duty in the Imperial Garden,

705
00:32:40,283 --> 00:32:41,464
I saw Prince Qi

706
00:32:42,003 --> 00:32:44,104
