711
00:32:54,924 --> 00:32:56,083
Otherwise, I wouldn't have

712
00:32:56,783 --> 00:32:57,864
hidden my identity

713
00:32:57,864 --> 00:32:59,424
and left my hometown.

714
00:33:03,964 --> 00:33:05,624
If what Wang Shiquan says is true,

715
00:33:06,164 --> 00:33:07,243
the Yan sisters

716
00:33:07,364 --> 00:33:08,944
