of the Yan sisters?

719
00:33:17,003 --> 00:33:18,364
There were a few maidservants

720
00:33:18,864 --> 00:33:20,783
serving Prince Qi,

721
00:33:21,783 --> 00:33:22,503
but

722
00:33:23,743 --> 00:33:25,023
none of them particularly stood out.

723
00:33:25,483 --> 00:33:27,364
