mention them.

724
00:33:28,303 --> 00:33:29,763
The Yan sisters might be

725
00:33:29,823 --> 00:33:30,843
the only ones who know the truth

726
00:33:30,843 --> 00:33:32,704
behind Prince Qi's death.

